meta {
  name: Submit Attendance
  type: http
  seq: 1
}

post {
  url: {{base_url}}/api/attendances/submit
  body: multipart-form
  auth: bearer
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{token}}
}

body:multipart-form {
  data: {"attendanceTimeInLatitude": -0.477961, "attendanceTimeInLongitude": 117.165098}
  image: @file(attendance_photo.jpg)
}

docs {
  ### Submit Attendance (Clock In)
  Mengirimkan data absensi menggunakan `multipart/form-data`.
  Endpoint ini memerlukan dua part:

  **Part 1 - `data` (Content-Type: application/json):**
  ```json
  {
    "username": "testuser",
    "attendanceTimeInLatitude": -0.477961,
    "attendanceTimeInLongitude": 117.165098
  }
  ```
  * `username`: Username akun yang sedang login
  * `attendanceTimeInLatitude`: Koordinat GPS Latitude saat clock-in
  * `attendanceTimeInLongitude`: Koordinat GPS Longitude saat clock-in

  **Part 2 - `image` (Content-Type: image/jpeg):**
  * File gambar hasil capture kamera (face verification photo)

  **Response (201 Created):**
  ```json
  {
    "status": "success",
    "message": "Attendance submitted successfully",
    "data": { ... }
  }
  ```
}
